SUGAR Power Clay Mask Stick 

Hey glow babies!

It's time to reset the button on stressed, dull skin. Indulge in these newly launched SUGAR Power Clay Stick Masks that promise you baby-soft, clear, and dewy skin. Available in 5 variants, these super-charged formulas fight down skin issues like clogged pores, blackheads, dryness, pesky spots, and oily-blotchy skin without any sticky mess or drama. The formula is unique, fuss-free, and packed with the wholesome goodness of natural ingredients such as grapefruit, watermelon extracts, charcoal powder, kaolin clay, flower extracts and so much more. Extremely easy to carry and use what you only need to do is wash your face, roll up the mask, apply and leave it good to dry for about 15-20 mins and wash it off. The smooth texture of the stick makes masking-on-the-go easy peasy! 

These Power Clay Stick Masks are 100% vegan and cruelty-free! Time to swipe on these beauties and flaunt your best skin ever.
